            "title": "盤中速報 - 道瓊指數大跌1%，報48920.7點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間28日01:18，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>下跌491.7點（或1%），暫報48920.70點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+2.03%</li><li>近 1 月：+1.56%</li><li>近 3 月：+4.05%</li><li>近 6 月：+10.18%</li><li>今年以來：+2.25%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>成分股以聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)領跌。聯合健康保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UNH:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UNH\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UNH-US</a>)下跌19.64%；耐吉(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NKE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NKE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NKE-US</a>)下跌2.4%；家得寶(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:HD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/HD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">HD-US</a>)下跌1.61%；美國運通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AXP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AXP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AXP-US</a>)下跌1.53%；沃爾瑪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WMT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WMT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WMT-US</a>)下跌1.38%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對穩健，蘋果(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>)上漲2.19%；微軟(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>)上漲1.86%；輝達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>)上漲1.7%；亞馬遜(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>)上漲1.57%；思科系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CSCO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CSCO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CSCO-US</a>)上漲1.56%。</p></section></main>",
